info.name: NovelCOVID API (github.com/NovelCOVID/API)
info.description:
API for Current cases and more stuff about COVID-19 or the Novel Coronavirus Strain.

- [Website](https://github.com/NovelCOVID/API)

query.description:

This includes iso codes, lat/long, a link to the country flag, cases, new cases, deaths, new deaths, recovered, active cases, critical cases, and cases/deaths per one million people. Data is updated every 10 minutes.
